column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objID, po.ra,p.ra, po.dec,p.dec, p.z, po.petroMag_u, po.petroMag_g, po.petroMag_r, po.petroMag_i, po.petroMag_z, po.petroRad_u, po.petroRad_g, po.petroRad_r, po.petroRad_i, po.petroRad_z FROM  Photoz p, Galaxy g, PhotoObj po, dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) n WHERE p.z BETWEEN # and # AND p.objID = po.objID AND po.objID = n.objID AND g.objID = p.objID
